# Docker

- Use specific image tags, not bare `latest`, unless the project standard says otherwise.
- Run application processes as non-root when feasible; set `USER` after installing deps.
- Minimize layers and image size; multi-stage builds for compiled apps when appropriate.
- Do not bake secrets into images; use build args and runtime env per project patterns.
- Document exposed ports and healthchecks when services are long-running.
